
1  

“Bende inyalo mako nyang’

gi olowu,

kata tueyo lewe gi tol?


2  Koso inyalo rwako tol e ume,

kata mako dhoge gi mbedo?


3  Bende dohombi mondo iweye odhi,

kata kwayi mondo ing’wonne?


4  Koso obiro loso kodi winjruok ni notini nyaka chieng’?


5  Koso ibiro tugo kode ka winyo manie sigol,

kata ka gimoro miywayo gi tol,

ma digalgo nyiri ma tiyoni?


6  Bende jolupo digo nengone?

Koso johala diyang’e mondo ong’iew ringe?


7  Bende inyalo chwowe gi bidhi mang’enymi tuch piene kod wiye?


8  Ka imule dichiel, to ok nichak imule kendo,

bende wiyi ok nowil gi lwenjno!


9  Ng’ato ang’ata moneno nyang’no, bwok mi gore piny.


10  Ka ng’ato okwinye, to oger malich,

kendo onge ng’at ma dihedhre chung’ e nyime.


11  Onge ng’ato e piny ngima manyalo monje, mi tony!


12  We awuonie kuom tiend nyang’no,

kendo anyisie kaka oduong’ kendo oratego.


13  Onge ng’at manyalo yang’o piene,

kata ma dituch sare ma ogeng’o dende.


14  Ere ng’ama dimi ong’am dhoge,

ma leke malich oriedoe?


15  Dier ng’eye olos gi sare,

moriedo machalo okumbni motue kanyakla,

kendo matek ka lwanda.


16  Moro ka moro ochom kuom wadgi matek

ma kata mana muya ok nyal kadho e kindgi.


17  Adier, oriwgi matek kanyakla,

ma onge gima nyalo pogogi.


18  Ka nyang’no ogir, to ler ema mil,

kendo wengeni rieny ka wang’ chieng’ ma thinyore.


19  Ligek mach kakni e dhoge, kendo pilni mach wuokie.


20  Iro dhuolore e ume mana ka ich yugi michwakogo agulu.


21  Muche moko mach! Adier, ligek mach wuok e dhoge.


22  Ng’ute tek malich,

omiyo ng’ato ka ng’ato moromo kode luor.


23  Onge kamoro ma reprep e piene,

to otek ka nyinyo, kendo ok nyal powe.


24  Chunye tek ka lwanda, kendo mana ka pong’ rego.


25  Ka oa malo, to koda ka joma rateke luoro mako.

Ee, kibaji goyogi nyang’eng’o.


26  Onge ligangla, kata tong’ kata asere, ma dihinye.


27  Gik molos gi chuma yomyomne mana ka tiang’,

kendo gik molos gi mula bende yomyomne mana ka yien motop.


28  Onge asere ma dimi oringi,

kendo kite mobayego chalone mana ka mihudhi.


29  Arungu to chalone mana gi tiang’,

kendo ka ji baye gi tong’, to onyiero anyiera.


30  Bwoye gwa, kendo gwaro piny mana ka ragwar.


31  Omiyo nam yienyo mana ka dakwon

kendo papni mana ka tap mo.


32  Koringo e nam, to ndache lokore rachar,

kendo nam lokore buoyo.


33  Onge gimoro e piny ngima minyalo pimo kode,

kendo ok oluoro gimoro.


34  Ochayo koda ka le magerie moloyo.

En e ruodh le duto.”

